org.apache.ignite.ml.naivebayes.gaussian

Class GaussianNaiveBayesModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.ml.naivebayes.gaussian.GaussianNaiveBayesModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AutoCloseable, DeployableObject, Exportable<GaussianNaiveBayesModel>, IgniteModel<Vector,Double>, Model<Vector,Double>, BayesModel<GaussianNaiveBayesModel,Vector,Double>

    public class GaussianNaiveBayesModel
extends Object
implements BayesModel<GaussianNaiveBayesModel,Vector,Double>, DeployableObject
    Simple naive Bayes model which predicts result value y belongs to a class C_k, k in [0..K] as p(C_k,y) = p(C_k)*p(y_1,C_k) *...*p(y_n,C_k) / p(y). Return the number of the most possible class.
